        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Right to Haul Act of 2014 - Exempts certain agricultural loads traveling on federal highways from federal vehicle weight limitations. Makes individual state weight limitations for&nbsp; agricultural commodities on state highways applicable to federal highways within the state's borders. <br /><br /><br /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
